Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了摧毁这支11区最大的武装势力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅总督对成田连山展开了包围作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在以压倒性镇压力为傲的布里塔尼亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为形势已定之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用红莲二式的辐射波动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使山中的地下水脉瞬间爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山崩发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论日本解放战线还是布里塔尼亚军主力部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都被泥石流卷入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去主力的科奈莉娅的部队被孤立了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要扭转情势的ZERO带领黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将科奈莉娅作为了目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人总是相信自己的胜利的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在时间与命运的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『相信』这种行为总是过于空虚  脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 11
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}成田攻防战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军的损失怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从信号上来看损失了20%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20%?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来指挥系统会出问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是玛里逊队  无法与阿历克斯将军取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2师团可以说是被全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有确定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有黑色骑士团出现的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜  说不定有出场机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不谨慎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我告诉你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  总之呢就等参谋部统合情报的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再决定对应措施吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山崩的范围之外  没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为身后的部队移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了容易被偷袭的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯血派在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  启动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会输给11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有荣耀自尊的布里塔尼亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威尔卿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  红莲前往预定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里由剩下的人突破  瞄准科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死守住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉山  还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死  冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  快行动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在这场战斗中活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就能成为战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那前方才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯血派阻止了他们?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在维蕾塔卿的指挥下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只有趁现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让总督向后退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空军掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督后面有什么正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无赖·改出击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这次山崩是人为造成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该可以到达科奈莉娅的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是讨回七年前的债的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上我们四圣剑的名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包围起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本解放战线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩击包围阵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要认为这只是普通的无赖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起七年前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时候可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我们也有KnightMare啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下  这里交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请暂时后退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿他们当祭品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交锋之后来九号地点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九号?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  就这样把ZERO压制住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  让卡莲回来会比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在如果变换配置的话作战会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此情况还是很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去就会和亲卫队交手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像科奈莉娅在下面受到了奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个部队的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们  好像是解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看透我们这里计划的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么应该可以拖住亲卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少将阁下  我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂  我等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下  现在请把兵力全部投入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能压制住布里塔尼亚本队的话就能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是逆转战局的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说11区有具有将军之才的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这人就是那个藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要和科奈莉亚总督汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  敌人的大本营就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果背后被攻击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部队就会出现损失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失去了公主的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗本身就会被结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲米娅副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这艘G1也出击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把总督…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  吉尔弗德队长也没有动就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅总督的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还设置了野战医院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:07:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有周围来避难的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  这艘G1 BASE是本阵的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督严命无论发生什么事都不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是特别派遣行动技术部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是随军的非正规军给我老老实实地待着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因如此所以很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常闲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲米娅副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给特派命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太显而易见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想要得到救出总督这个功绩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就凭一台机体就能改变状况的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不会辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只不过是个编号住民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  所以说让我们试试看也好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算失败了你们那边也没什么损失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我说你们有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  一定不辜负您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙  真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果ZERO是我猜的那种人的话一定会出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有相信他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO改变行进路线了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在就去援助你们那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些还是要注意ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把路线的情报给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是ZERO他们的预测路线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想把藤堂他们引去的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听见了  吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向导兵器  Z01 Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用SANDBOOT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用最大战速沿液状斜面上升
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援总督
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  想要问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你极端讨厌人的死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却愿意在军队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让人死才会在军队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种纯真总有一天会害死你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是个无能的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是普通的CUSTOM机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[CUSTOM机：指一般机体的强化机种]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见没有  科奈莉娅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该庆祝我们的再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  在此之前希望你能向我们投降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事想要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一说  你的援军来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的胜利哦  科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒这家伙就能走上胜利之路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是能干的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从背后攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那你是说你们的作战不卑鄙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重整情势之前竟然受到夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去会到不了公主那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把敌人的援军击溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变换旋回活杀自在阵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去科奈莉娅殿下会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的骑士吉尔弗德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能和达尔顿一起辅佐由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会投降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一名皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有战斗到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科…科奈莉娅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  无聊的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一样乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用VARIS把之间的障碍都毁掉这种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是特派
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那架Lancelot的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  那架KnightMare是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是新宿和河口那个时候的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是吗  又是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲二式把白壳的家伙毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的突破力是个障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我攻击ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿的债我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Lancelot一样高速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这种武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挡下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇  红莲怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不修理的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军  向撤退路线移动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再下去会成为消耗战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去追ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是能源没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  撤退真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了已经是事实了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有把日本解放战线作为诱饵  逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我讨厌这种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类不是游戏的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO应该也不是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也成了棋盘上被使用的棋子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对于布里塔尼亚的愤怒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知晓愤怒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该也知晓悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特派报告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:13:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始俘获
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO  你有恩于我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的行动也有人被救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道很多11区住民在背后支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是  新宿的  密封舱里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对这个男人出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是  ZERO的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是KnightMare啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你死了我会很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是间接接触
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有尝试一下的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那种意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  难道你对驾驶员使用Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是给他看打击影像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看到了些什么我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地欠着你的情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  和之前的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要到我的里面来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点…逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的行动停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在和少将他们汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助他们逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下  我现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔弗德  通报全军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有理由再赌上我们将士的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持战斗态势
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缓缓撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是我们输了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚要对付解放战线已经竭尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我们也确实得到了逃跑的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和无赖无法联系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人  果然不是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口的再生速度不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿的时候的确也被击中了额头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克洛维斯私下在研究的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和布里塔尼亚应该没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,vital sign和人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[vital sign：生命征兆 如脉搏 呼吸 体温 心跳等]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血液样本稍后再检查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口也拍一下照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是没有抓住ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本解放战线设下了防卫线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是混在里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把什么当作盾牌来保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到他能量耗尽之前一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以多花了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体状态不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为处于暴走状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是哥哥部队该有的失态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经把碎片取出了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也帮你洗过伤口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子的确是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不需要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是在无聊的地方执著于自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏这样知道了些好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴趣真坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷听这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比C.C.像人类多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我像人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在名字这种
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字…什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好机会所以我说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止也一直是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括Geass的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次被人感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要还礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再叫一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像刚才一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重视的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的包含心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呢  完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直率与体贴的心意也不够
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发音也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是缺少温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个任性的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是军人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明部队崩溃到这种程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接的人貌似来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的成员先…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道雪为什么是白的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为白色的雪很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把科奈莉娅逼入绝境的某种条件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.67,0:23:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了弥补这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能我自己必须跨越某种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.68,0:24:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须前往该去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果为此这是必须的话  我…
